4:34 “Ayii we! Duhuriye he Yesu w'i Nazareti? Uje kuturimbura? Ndakuzi uri Uwera w'Imana.”
4:35 Yesu aramucyaha ati “Hora muvemo.” Dayimoni amutura hasi hagati yabo, amuvamo atagize icyo amutwara.
4:36 Bose barumirwa barabazanya bati “Mbega rino jambo ni jambo ki? Arategekesha abadayimoni ubutware n'ububasha bakavamo!” 
4:37 Inkuru ye yamamara hose mu gihugu gihereranye n'aho.
4:38 Arahaguruka asohoka mu isinagogi, yinjira mu nzu ya Simoni. Nyirabukwe wa Simoni yari arwaye ubuganga bwinshi, nuko baramumwingingira. 
4:39 Amuhagarara iruhande acyaha ubuganga bumuvamo, muri ako kanya arahaguruka arabagaburira.
4:40 Nuko izuba rigiye kurenga, abafite abarwayi bose barwaye indwara zitari zimwe barabamuzanira. Abarambikaho ibiganza umwe umwe arabakiza. 
4:41 Kandi n'abadayimoni bava muri benshi bataka bati “Uri Umwana w'Imana.”
4:42 Bukeye ajya mu butayu, abantu benshi baramushaka bagera aho ari, bashaka kumubuza ngo atava muri bo. 
4:43 Ariko arababwira ati “Nkwiriye kwigisha ubutumwa bwiza bw'Imana no mu yindi midugudu, kuko ari ibyo natumiwe.”
4:44 Nuko yigishiriza mu masinagogi y'i Galilaya.
5:1   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 13.1-2; Mar 3.9-10; 4.1  
5:2 Abona amato abiri atsītse ku nkombe y'inyanja, ariko abarobyi bari bayavuyemo bamesa inshundura zabo. 
5:3 Yikira mu bwato bumwe bwari ubwa Simoni, amusaba kubutsuraho hato ngo buve ku nkombe, aricara yigisha abantu ari mu bwato.
