5:5   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Yoh 21.3  
5:6  Babikoze bafata ifi nyinshi cyane, ndetse inshundura zabo zenda gucika. 
5:7 Barembuza bagenzi babo bari mu bundi bwato ngo baze babatabare, baraza buzuza amato yombi bituma yenda kurengerwa. 
5:8 Simoni Petero ngo abibone atyo yikubita imbere ya Yesu ati “Va aho ndi Databuja, kuko ndi umunyabyaha!”
5:9 Kuko ubwe yari yumiwe n'abari kumwe na we bose babonye izo fi bafashe, 
5:10 na Yakobo na Yohana bene Zebedayo bari bafatanije na Simoni na bo birabatangaza. Yesu abwira Simoni ati “Witinya, uhereye none uzajya uroba abantu.”
5:11 Bamaze kugeza amato yabo ku nkombe, basiga byose baramukurikira.
5:12 Bukeye ubwo Yesu yari ari mu mudugudu, haza umuntu urwaye ibibembe byinshi. Abonye Yesu yikubita hasi yubamye, aramwinginga ati “Databuja, washaka wabasha kunkiza.”
5:13 Yesu arambura ukuboko amukoraho, ati “Ndabishaka kira.” Muri ako kanya indwara ye imuvamo. 
5:14   
5:15 Nyamara inkuru ye irushaho kwamamara, iteraniro ry'abantu benshi riteranira kumwumva no gukizwa indwara zabo, 
5:16 ariko we abavamo yiherera mu butayu asenga.
5:17 Nuko ku munsi umwe muri iyo yarigishaga, Abafarisayo n'abigishamategeko bari bicaye aho bavuye mu birorero byose by'i Galilaya n'i Yudaya n'i Yerusalemu, kandi imbaraga z'Umwami Imana zari muri we zo kubakiza. 
5:18 Nuko abagabo bazana umuntu mu ngobyi waremaye, bashaka kumwinjiza ngo bamushyire imbere ye. 
5:19 Babuze aho bamwinjiriza kuko abantu bahuzuye, burira hejuru y'inzu bamucisha mu mategura, bamumanurana n'ingobyi hagati yabo imbere ya Yesu. 
5:20 Abonye kwizera kwabo aravuga ati “Wa mugabo we, ibyaha byawe urabibabariwe.”
5:21 Abanditsi n'Abafarisayo batangira kwiburanya bati “Uyu ni nde wigereranije? Ni nde ushobora kubabarira ibyaha uretse Imana yonyine?”
5:22 Maze Yesu amenya ibyo biburanya, arababaza ati “Muriburanya iki mu mitima yanyu? 
5:23 Icyoroshye ni ikihe, ari ukuvuga nti ‘Ibyaha byawe urabibabariwe’, cyangwa nti ‘Byuka ugende’? 
5:24 Ariko mumenye yuko Umwana w'umuntu afite ubutware mu isi bwo kubabarira abantu ibyaha.” Nuko abwira icyo kirema ati “Ndagutegetse, byuka wikorere ingobyi yawe utahe.”
5:25 Muri ako kanya abyuka imbere yabo, yikorera ingobyi yari aryamyeho, ataha ahimbaza Imana. 
5:26 Bose barumirwa bahimbaza Imana, baterwa n'ubwoba bati “Uyu munsi wa none tubonye ibidutangaza.”
5:27 Nuko ibyo bishize arasohoka, abona umukoresha w'ikoro witwaga Lewi yicaye aho yakoresherezaga ikoro, aramubwira ati “Nkurikira.” 
5:28 Na we asiga byose, arahaguruka aramukurikira.
5:29 Lewi amujyana iwe, amutekeshereza ibyokurya barasangira. Hari n'inteko y'abakoresha b'ikoro benshi n'abandi bari bararitswe, bicarana na bo. 
5:30   
5:31 Yesu arabasubiza ati “Abazima si bo bakwiriye umuvuzi, keretse abarwayi. 
5:32 Sinazanywe no guhamagara abakiranuka, keretse abanyabyaha ngo bihane.”
5:33 Baramubwira bati “Abigishwa ba Yohana biyiriza ubusa kenshi bagasenga, n'Abafarisayo ni uko, naho abawe barya bakanywa!”
5:34 Yesu arababaza ati “Mbese mwabasha kwiriza ubusa abasangwa bakiri kumwe n'umukwe? 
5:35 Icyakora iminsi izaza, ubwo umukwe azabavanwamo, ni bwo baziyiriza ubusa.”
5:36 Maze abacira umugani ati “Nta muntu utabura igitambaro ku mwenda mushya ngo akidode mu mwenda ushaje, uwagira aty, cyaca wa wundi cyadozweho, kandi igitambaro atabuye ku mushya nticyahwana n'ushaje. 
5:37 Kandi nta muntu usuka vino y'umutobe mu mifuka y'impu ishaje, uwagira atyo vino y'umutobe yaturitsa iyo mifuka, vino igasandara hasi n'imifuka ikononekara. 
5:38 Ahubwo ibikwiye ni ugusuka vino y'umutobe mu mifuka mishya. 
5:39 Kandi nta muntu wanyoye vino ihiye washaka idahiye, kuko agira ngo ‘Ihiye ni yo nziza.’ ”
6:1   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Guteg 23.26  
6:2 Nuko Abafarisayo bamwe barababaza bati “Ni iki gitumye mukora ibizira ku isabato?”
6:3   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    1 Sam 21.1-6  
6:4   
6:5 Kandi arababwira ati “Umwana w'umuntu ni Umwami w'isabato.”
6:6 Nuko ku yindi sabato yinjira mu isinagogi arigisha. Asangamo umuntu unyunyutse ukuboko kw'iburyo. 
6:7 Abanditsi n'Abafarisayo bagenza Yesu ngo barebe ko amukiza ku isabato, babone uko bamurega. 
6:8 Ariko amenya ibyo batekereza, abwira uwo muntu unyunyutse ukuboko ati “Haguruka uhagarare hagati mu bantu.” Arahaguruka arahagarara. 
6:9 Nuko Yesu arababwira ati “Ndababaza yuko amategeko yemera gukora neza ku isabato cyangwa ko akora nabi, gukiza umuntu cyangwa kumwica?” 
6:10 Abararanganyamo amaso bose abwira wa wundi ati “Rambura ukuboko kwawe.” Arakurambura kurakira.
6:11 Maze bazabiranywa n'uburakari, bajya inama y'uko bazagenza Yesu.
6:12 Nuko muri iyo minsi avayo ajya ku musozi gusenga, akesha ijoro asenga Imana. 
6:13 Ijoro rikeye ahamagara abigishwa be, atoranyamo cumi na babiri abita intumwa: 
6:14 Simoni uwo yise Petero na Andereya mwene se, na Yakobo na Yohana, na Filipo na Barutolomayo, 
6:15 na Matayo na Toma na Yakobo mwene Alufayo, na Simoni witwa Zelote 
6:16 na Yuda mwene Yakobo, na Yuda Isikariyota wahindutse umugambanyi.
6:17 Amanukana na bo, ahagarara aharinganiye ari kumwe n'abigishwa be benshi, n'abantu benshi bavuye i Yudaya hose n'i Yerusalemu, no mu gihugu cy'i Tiro n'i Sidoni gihereranye n'Inyanja Nini, bazanywe no kumwumva no gukizwa indwara zabo, 
6:18 kandi n'abababazwaga n'abadayimoni arabakiza. 
6:19 Abantu bose bashaka kumukoraho, kuko imbaraga yamuvagamo ikabakiza bose.
6:20 Yuburira abigishwa be amaso arababwira ati
6:21 Hahirwa mwebwe mushonje ubu,
