6:23   
6:24 Ariko muzabona ishyano mwa batunzi mwe,
6:25 Namwe muzabona ishyano mwebwe abahāze ubu,
6:26 “Muzabona ishyano abantu nibabavuga neza, kuko ari ko ba sekuruza wabo bagenje abahanuzi b'ibinyoma.
6:27 “Ariko ndababwira mwebwe abumva, mukunde abanzi banyu, mugirire neza ababanga, 
6:28 mwifurize neza ababavuma, musabire ababangiriza. 
6:29 Ugukubise mu musaya umuhindurire n'uwa kabiri, uzakwaka umwitero ntuzamwime ikanzu. 
6:30 Ugusaba wese umuhe, unyaga ibyawe ntuzabimwake ukundi. 
6:31   
6:32 “Nimukunda ababakunda muzashimwa iki? Abanyabyaha na bo bakunda ababakunda. 
6:33 Kandi nimugirira neza abayibagirira muzashimwa iki? Abanyabyaha na bo ni ko bakora. 
6:34 Kandi nimuguriza abo mutekereza ko bazabaguzurira muzashimwa iki? Abanyabyaha na bo ni ko baguriza abandi banyabyaha, kugira ngo bazaguzurirwe ibihwanye n'ibyo babagurije. 
6:35 Ahubwo mukunde abanzi banyu, mubagirire neza, mugurize abantu mudatekereza ko bazabishyura. Ni bwo ingororano zanyu zizaba nyinshi, namwe muzaba abana b'Isumbabyose kuko igirira neza ababi n'indashima. 
6:36 Mugirirane imbabazi nk'uko So na we azigira.
6:37 “Kandi ntimugacire abandi urubanza mu mitima yanyu kugira ngo namwe mutazarucirwa, kandi ntimugatsindishe namwe mutazatsindishwa. Mubabarire abandi namwe muzababarirwa, 
6:38 mutange namwe muzahabwa. Urugero rwiza rutsindagiye, rucugushije, rusesekaye ni rwo muzagererwa, kuko urugero mugeramo ari rwo muzagererwamo namwe.”
6:39   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 15.14  
6:40   
6:41 “Ni iki gituma ureba agatotsi kari mu jisho rya mwene so, ukirengagiza umugogo uri mu jisho ryawe? 
6:42 Wabasha ute kubwira mwene so uti ‘Mwene data, henga ngutokore agatotsi kari mu jisho ryawe’, nawe nturebe umugogo uri mu ryawe? Wa ndyarya we, banza wikuremo umugogo uri mu jisho ryawe, abe ari ho ubona uko utokora agatotsi kari mu jisho rya mwene so.
6:43 “Kuko ari nta giti cyiza cyera imbuto mbi, cyangwa igiti kibi cyera imbuto nziza. 
6:44  Igiti cyose kimenyekanishwa n'imbuto zacyo: ntibasoroma imbuto z'umutini ku mugenge, cyangwa imizabibu ku mufatangwe. 
6:45   
6:46 “Mumpamagarira iki muti ‘Databuja, Databuja’, nyamara ntimukore ibyo mvuga? 
6:47 Umuntu wese uza aho ndi, akumva amagambo yanjye akayakomeza, ndabereka uko asa: 
6:48 asa n'umuntu wubaka inzu, agacukura hasi cyane akageza urufatiro ku rutare. Nuko umugezi wuzuye uhururira kuri iyo nzu ariko ntiwabasha kuyinyeganyeza, kuko yubatswe ku rutare. 
6:49 Naho rero uwumva ntabikore, asa n'umuntu wubatse inzu ku butaka adacukuye urufatiro. Nuko umugezi uyihururiraho ako kanya iragwa, kandi kurimbuka kwayo kwabaye kubi.”
7:1 Nuko ayo magambo yose amaze kuyabwira abantu, ajya i Kaperinawumu. 
7:2 Hariyo umutware utwara umutwe w'abasirikare, yari afite umugaragu we akunda cyane, wari urwaye yenda gupfa. 
7:3 Uwo yumvise inkuru ya Yesu, amutumaho abakuru b'Abayuda kumwinginga ngo aze gukiza umugaragu we. 
7:4 Na bo basanze Yesu baramuhendahenda bati “Ni umuntu ukwiriye ko umugirira utyo 
7:5 kuko akunda ubwoko bwacu, ndetse n'isinagogi yacu ni we wayitwubakiye.”
7:6 Yesu ajyana na bo, ageze hafi y'inzu uwo mutware w'abasirikare amutumaho incuti ze ati “Nyagasani, ntiwirushye kuko bitankwiriye ko winjira mu nzu yanjye, 
7:7 ni cyo gitumye ntekereza ko bitankwiriye ndetse ko nza aho uri ubwanjye. Ahubwo tegeka, umugaragu wanjye arakira. 
7:8 Kuko nanjye ndi umuntu utwarwa n'abandi, mfite n'abasirikare ntwara. Iyo mbwiye umwe nti ‘Genda’ aragenda, nabwira undi nti ‘Ngwino’ akaza, nabwira umugaragu wanjye nti ‘Kora iki’ akagikora.”
7:9 Yesu abyumvise aramutangarira, ahindukirira abantu bamukurikiye ati “Ndababwira yuko ntabwo nari nabona kwizera kungana gutya, habe no mu Bisirayeli.”
7:10 Izo ntumwa zisubiye mu nzu zisanga uwo mugaragu akize.
7:11 Bukeye ajya mu mudugudu witwa Nayini, abigishwa be n'abantu benshi bajyana na we. 
7:12 Ageze hafi y'irembo ry'umudugudu ahura n'abikoreye ikiriba. Uwari wapfuye yari umwana w'ikinege, kandi nyina yari umupfakazi, abantu benshi bo muri uwo mudugudu bari bamuherekeje. 
7:13 Umwami Yesu amubonye amugirira imbabazi aramubwira ati “Wirira.” 
7:14 Yegera ikiriba agikoraho, abacyikoreye barahagarara. Ati “Muhungu, ndagutegetse byuka.” 
7:15 Uwari upfuye arabaduka atangira kuvuga, Yesu amusubiza nyina.
7:16 Bose baterwa n'ubwoba bahimbaza Imana bati “Umuhanuzi ukomeye abonetse muri twe”, kandi bati “Imana igendereye ubwoko bwayo.”
7:17 Iyo nkuru y'ibyo yakoze yamamara i Yudaya hose, no mu gihugu cyose gihereranye n'aho.
7:18 Nuko abigishwa ba Yohana bamutekerereza ibyo byose. 
7:19 Yohana ahamagara babiri muri bo, abatuma ku Mwami Yesu ati “Mbese ni wowe wa wundi ukwiriye kuza, cyangwa dutegereze undi?”
7:20 Basohoye kuri Yesu baramubwira bati “Yohana Umubatiza akudutumyeho ngo ‘Ni wowe wa wundi ukwiriye kuza, cyangwa dutegereze undi?’ ”
7:21 Nuko muri uwo mwanya akiza benshi indwara n'ibyago n'abadayimoni, n'impumyi nyinshi arazihumura. 
7:22  Arabasubiza ati “Nimugende mubwire Yohana ibyo mubonye n'ibyo mwumvise. Impumyi zirahumuka, abacumbagira baragenda, ababembe barakira, ibipfamatwi birumva, abapfuye barazurwa, abakene barabwirwa ubutumwa bwiza. 
7:23 Kandi hahirwa uwo ibyanjye bitazagusha.”
7:24 Intumwa za Yohana zimaze kugenda, atangira kuvugana n'abantu ibya Yohana ati “Mwajyanywe mu butayu no kureba iki? Ni urubingo ruhungabanywa n'umuyaga? 
7:25 Ariko se mwagiye kureba iki? Ni umuntu wambaye imyenda yorohereye? Erega abambara imyenda y'abarimbyi n'abagaburirwa ibyiza baba mu ngo z'abami! 
7:26 Ariko se mwajyanywe no kureba iki? Ni umuhanuzi? Ni koko, kandi ndababwira ko aruta umuhanuzi cyane. 
7:27   
7:28 Ndababwira yuko mu babyawe n'abagore ari nta wuruta Yohana, nyamara umuto mu bwami bw'Imana aramuruta.”
7:29   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 21.32; Luka 3.12  
7:30 Ariko Abafarisayo n'abigishamategeko ubwo batabatijwe na we, bivukije inama z'Imana.
7:31 “Mbese ab'iki gihe ndabagereranya n'iki? Kandi bameze nk'iki? 
7:32 Ni nk'abahungu bato bicaye mu maguriro bahamagarana bati ‘Twabavugirije imyironge ntimwabyina, twaboroze ntimwarira.’ 
7:33 Yohana Umubatiza yaje atarya umutsima, atanywa vino, muravuga muti ‘Afite dayimoni.’ 
7:34 Umwana w'umuntu aje arya, anywa, muravuga ngo ‘Dore iki kirura cy'umunywi w'inzoga, n'incuti y'abakoresha b'ikoro n'abanyabyaha.’ 
7:35 Ariko ubwenge bugaragazwa n'abana babwo bose, ko ari ubw'ukuri.”
7:36 Umwe mu Bafarisayo aramurarika ngo asangire na we, yinjira mu nzu ye aricara ngo arye. 
7:37  Umugore wo muri uwo mudugudu wari umunyabyaha, amenya yuko arīra mu nzu y'uwo Mufarisayo, azana umukondo w'amavuta meza ameze nk'amadahano, 
7:38 ahagarara inyuma ye hafi y'ibirenge bye arira, atangira kumutonyangiriza amarira ku birenge abihanaguza umusatsi we, asoma ibirenge bye, abisīga ayo mavuta. 
7:39 Uwo Mufarisayo wamurarits, abibonye aribwira ati “Uyu muntu iyo aba umuhanuzi, yajyaga kumenya uyu mugore umukozeho uwo ari we kandi uko ameze, ko ari umunyabyaha.”
7:40 Yesu aramusubiza ati “Simoni, mfite icyo nkubwira.”
7:41 Ati “Hariho umuntu wagurizaga, wari ufite abantu babiri bamubereyemo imyenda. Umwe yarimo umwenda w'idenariyo magana atanu, undi arimo mirongo itanu. 
7:42 Ariko kuko bari babuze ubwishyu azibaharira bombi. Mbese muri abo bombi uwarushije undi kumukunda ni nde?”
7:43 Simoni aramusubiza ati “Ngira ngo ni uwo yahariye inyinshi.”
7:44 Akebuka uwo mugore abwira Simoni ati “Urareba uyu mugore? Ninjiye mu nzu yawe ntiwampa amazi yo koza ibirenge, ariko uyu we antonyangirije amarira ku birenge, abihanaguza umusatsi we. 
7:45 Ntiwansomye, ariko aho ninjiriye uyu ntiyahwemye kunsoma ibirenge. 
7:46 Ntiwansīze amavuta mu mutwe, ariko uyu we ansīze amavuta meza ku birenge. 
7:47 Ni cyo gitumye nkubwira yuko ababariwe bya byaha bye byinshi, kuko yagize urukundo rwinshi. Ariko ubabarirwa bike, akunda buke.”
7:48 Abwira umugore ati “Ubabariwe ibyaha byawe.”
7:49 Nuko abasangiraga na we batangira kubazanya bati “Uyu ni nde, ubabarira n'ibyaha?”
7:50 Abwira uwo mugore ati “Kwizera kwawe kuragukijije, genda amahoro.”
8:1 Hanyuma ajya mu midugudu n'ibirorero yigisha, avuga ubutumwa bwiza bw'ubwami bw'Imana ari kumwe n'abigishwa be cumi na babiri, 
8:2  n'abagore bamwe bakijijwe abadayimoni n'indwara, barimo Mariya witwaga Magadalena wirukanywemo abadayimoni barindwi, 
8:3 na Yowana muka Kuza igisonga cya Herode, na Suzana n'abandi bagore benshi babafashishaga ibyabo.
8:4 Nuko abantu benshi bamusanga bavuye mu midugudu yose, bamaze guterana abacira umugani ati 
8:5 “Umubibyi yasohoye imbuto, akibiba zimwe zigwa mu nzira barazikandagira, inyoni zo mu kirere zirazitoragura. 
8:6 Izindi zigwa ku kāra, zimaze kumera ziruma kuko zihabuze amazi. 
8:7 Izindi zigwa mu mahwa, amahwa amerana na zo araziniga. 
8:8 Izindi zigwa mu butaka bwiza ziramera, zera imbuto imwe ijana, indi ijana, bityo bityo.”
8:9 Nuko abigishwa be bamusobanuza uwo mugani. 
8:10   
8:11 “Dore iby'uwo mugani ni ibi: imbuto ni ijambo ry'Imana. 
8:12 Izo mu nzira, abo ni bo bumva ijambo hanyuma Umwanzi akaza agakura ijambo mu mitima yabo, kugira ngo batizera ngo bakizwe. 
8:13 Izaguye ku kāra, abo ni bo bumva ijambo bakaryemera banezerewe, ariko ntibagire imizi. Bīzera umwanya muto, maze ibibagerageza byabageraho bagasubira inyuma. 
8:14 Izaguye mu mahwa ni bo bumva ijambo, maze bakigenda amaganya n'ubutunzi n'ibinezeza byo muri ubu bugingo bikabaniga, ntibere imbuto nziza. 
8:15 Izo mu butaka bwiza, abo ni bo bumva ijambo bakarifata neza mu mitima inyuzwe myiza, bakera imbuto ku bwo kwihangana.
