8:19 Nuko nyina na bene se baza aho ari, ariko ntibabasha kumugeraho kuko abateraniye aho ari benshi. 
8:20 Abantu baramubwira bati “Nyoko na bene so bahagaze hanze baragushaka.”
8:21 Na we arabasubiza ati “Mama na bene Data ni aba bumva ijambo ry'Imana bakarikomeza.”
8:22 Nuko ku munsi umwe, yikirana mu bwato n'abigishwa be arababwira ati “Twambuke tujye hakurya y'inyanja.” Baratsuka. 
8:23 Bakigenda arasinzira, mu nyanja hamanuka umuyaga urimo ishuheri ubwato bwenda kurengerwa n'amazi, bajya mu kaga. 
8:24 Baraza baramukangura bati “Databuja, Databuja! Turapfuye.”
8:25 Arababaza ati “Kwizera kwanyu kuri he?”
8:26 Nuko bafata hakurya mu gihugu cy'Abagadareni, giteganye n'i Galilaya. 
