15:1   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Luka 5.29-30  
15:2 Abafarisayo n'abanditsi barabyivovotera bati “Uyu yiyegereza abanyabyaha, kandi agasangira na bo.”
15:3 Abacira uyu mugani ati 
15:4 “Ni nde muri mwe waba afite intama ijana akazimiza imwe muri zo, ntasige izindi mirongo urwenda n'icyenda mu gasozi, akajya gushaka iyazimiye kugeza aho ari buyibonere? 
15:5 Iyo ayibonye ayiterera ku bitugu yishimye, 
