15:8 “Cyangwa umugore waba afite ibice cumi by'ifeza, yaburamo kimwe ntiyakongeza itabaza, agakubura mu nzu, akagira umwete wo gushaka kugeza aho akibonera? 
15:9 Iyo akibonye ahamagara incuti ze n'abaturanyi be akababwira ati ‘Twishimane kuko mbonye igice nari nabuze.’ 
15:10 Ndababwira yuko ari ko haba umunezero mwinshi imbere y'abamarayika b'Imana, bishimira umunyabyaha umwe wihannye.”
15:11 Kandi arababwira ati “Hariho umuntu wari ufite abahungu babiri. 
15:12 Umuhererezi abwira se ati ‘Data, mpa umugabane w'ibintu unkwiriye.’ Nuko agabanya amatungo ye. 
15:13 Iminsi mike ishize umuhererezi ateranya ibintu bye byose, aragenda ajya mu gihugu cya kure, yayisha ibintu bye ubugoryi bwe. 
15:14 Abimaze byose inzara nyinshi itera muri icyo gihugu, atangira gukena. 
15:15 Aragenda ahakwa ku muntu wo muri icyo gihugu, amwohereza mu gikingi cye kuragira ingurube. 
