15:22 Ariko se abwira abagaragu be ati ‘Mwihute muzane vuba umwenda uruta iyindi muwumwambike, mumwambike n'impeta ku rutoki n'inkweto mu birenge, 
15:23 muzane n'ikimasa kibyibushye mukibage turye twishime, 
15:24 kuko uyu mwana wanjye yari yarapfuye none akaba azutse, yari yarazimiye none dore arabonetse.’ Nuko batangira kwishima.
15:25 “Ariko umwana we w'imfura yari ari mu murima, amaze kuza ageze hafi y'urugo yumva abacuranga n'ababyina. 
