24:12 Maze Petero arahaguruka yirukanka ajya ku gituro, arunama arungurukamo, abona imyenda y'ibitare iri yonyine. Asubira iwe atangazwa n'ibyabaye.
24:13 Nuko uwo munsi babiri muri bo bajyaga mu kirorero cyitwa Emawusi. (Kuva i Yerusalemu kugerayo ni nka sitadiyo mirongo itandatu.)</span><span class="note f"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body"><span class="fk">sitadiyo mirongo itandatu </span><span class="ft"> ni urugendo rw'amasaha abiri n'igice.
24:14 Nuko baganira ibyabaye byose. 
24:15 Bakiganira babazanya, Yesu arabegera ajyana na bo, 
24:16 Ariko amaso yabo arabuzwa ngo batamumenya. 
24:17 Arababaza ati “Muragenda mubazanya ibiki?”
24:18 Umwe muri bo witwaga Kilewopa aramusubiza ati “Mbese ni wowe wenyine mu bashyitsi b'i Yerusalemu, utazi ibyahabaye muri iyi minsi?”
24:19 Arababaza ati “Ni ibiki?”
24:20 kandi twavuganaga uburyo abatambyi bakuru n'abatware bacu, bamutanze ngo acirwe urubanza rwo gupfa bakamubamba, 
24:21 kandi twiringiraga yuko ari we uzacungura Abisirayeli. Uretse ibyo, dore uyu munsi ni uwa gatatu uhereye aho ibyo byabereye. 
24:22 None abagore bo muri twe badutangaje, kuko bazindutse bajya ku gituro 
24:23 ntibasangamo intumbi ye. Nuko baraza batubwira ko babonekewe n'abamarayika, bakababwira ko ari muzima. 
24:24 Kandi bamwe mu bari bari kumwe na twe bagiye ku gituro basanga ari ko biri, uko abagore batubwiye, ariko we ntibamubona.”
24:25 Arababwira ati “Mwa bapfu mwe, imitima yanyu itinze cyane kwizera ibyo abahanuzi bavuze byose. 
24:26 None se Kristo ntiyari akwiriye kubabazwa atyo, ngo abone kwinjira mu bwiza bwe?” 
24:27 Atangirira kuri Mose no ku bahanuzi bose, abasobanurira mu byanditswe byose ibyanditswe kuri we.
24:28 Bageze bugufi bw'ikirorero bajyagamo, agira nk'ushaka kugicaho. 
24:29 Baramuhata bati “Se waretse tukagumana kuko bwije kandi umunsi ukaba ukuze?” Nuko arinjira ngo agumane na bo. 
24:30 Yicaye ngo asangire na bo, yenda umutsima arawushimira, arawumanyagura arawubaha. 
24:31 Amaso yabo arahumuka baramumenya, maze aburira imbere yabo ntibongera kumubona. 
24:32 Baravugana bati “Yewe, ntiwibuka ukuntu imitima yacu yari ikeye, ubwo yavuganaga natwe turi mu nzira adusobanurira ibyanditswe!”
24:33 Uwo mwanya barahaguruka basubira i Yerusalemu, basanga abo cumi n'umwe bateranye hamwe n'abandi, 
24:34 bumva bavuga bati “Ni ukuri Umwami Yesu yazutse, ndetse yabonekeye Simoni.”
24:35 Nuko ba bandi babiri na bo babatekerereza ibyabereye mu nzira, n'uburyo bamumenyeshejwe n'uko amanyaguye umutsima.
24:36 Bakivuga ibyo, Yesu ahagarara hagati yabo arababwira ati “Amahoro abe muri mwe.”
24:37 Maze barikanga, bagira ubwoba bwinshi bagira ngo ni umuzimu babonye. 
24:38 Arababwira ati “Ikibahagaritse imitima ni iki, kandi ni iki gitumye mwiburanya mu mitima yanyu? 
24:39 Nimurebe ibiganza byanjye n'ibirenge byanjye, mumenye ko ari jye ubwanjye. Ndetse nimunkoreho murebe, kuko umuzimu atagira umubiri n'amagufwa nk'ibyo mundebana.”
24:40 Avuze ibyo abereka ibiganza bye n'ibirenge bye. 
24:41 Nuko ibinezaneza bikibabujije kubyemera, bagitangara arababaza ati “Hari icyo kurya mufite hano?” 
24:42 Bamuha igice cy'ifi yokeje, 
24:43 aracyākira akirīra imbere yabo.
24:44 Maze arababwira ati “Aya ni amagambo nababwiraga nkiri kumwe namwe, yuko ibyanditswe kuri jye byose mu mategeko ya Mose, no mu byahanuwe no muri Zaburi bikwiriye gusohora.”
24:45 Maze abungura ubwenge ngo basobanukirwe n'ibyanditswe, 
24:46 ati “Ni ko byanditswe ko Kristo akwiriye kubabazwa no kuzuka ku munsi wa gatatu, 
24:47 kandi ko kwihana no kubabarirwa ibyaha bikwiriye kubwirwa amahanga yose mu izina rye, bahereye kuri Yerusalemu. 
24:48 Ni mwe bagabo b'ibyo. 
